data.title: José Joaquim Emérico Lobo de Mesquita
meta_keywords: José Joaquim Emérico Lobo de Mesquita
data.meta_description: José Joaquim Emérico Lobo de Mesquita. Composer: Symphonia Colonialis. José Joaquim Emérico Lobo de Mesquita was born on 12 October 1746 in Vila do Príncipe, Minas Gerais, Brazil. José Joaquim Emérico was a composer, known for Symphonia Colonialis (1991). José Joaquim Emérico died in April 1805 in Rio de Janeiro, Brazil.
